scene.message:
Ayase: I've seen this{nl}
classroom — in an old framed{nl}
photo in the principal's{nl}
office.{waitkey}{clearbox}This is the wooden schoolhouse{nl}
from before the current{nl}
building was built.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: That's Ayase for you.{waitkey}No surprise, given how many{nl}
times she's been lectured in{nl}
the principal's office.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: The warmth of wood{wait_fr:30},{nl}
the coziness of handcraft{wait_fr:30}{nl}
...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}as if{wait_fr:15} there's{nl}
any of that, argh!!{waitkey}{clearbox}The drafts are brutal and{nl}
it reeks of mold...{waitkey}I want a piping-hot bath~{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: What an Antique{nl}
building.{waitkey}{clearbox}If not for circumstances, I'd{nl}
love to take a slow look{nl}
around.{waitkey}{ret}
